OL,3,CParliament to vote on granting
OL,4,CGovernment control of British Steel
OL,6,FMPs are set to vote on whether to
OL,7,Fgrant the Government control of
OL,8,FBritish Steel as emergency legislation
OL,9,Fpaving the way for nationalisation
OL,10,Fcomes before Parliament.
OL,12,FBoth the Commons and the Lords will
OL,13,Fbreak from Easter recess for a highly
OL,14,Funusual Saturday sitting to debate a
OL,15,FBill aimed at blocking the company's
OL,16,FChinese owners, Jingye, from closing
OL,17,Fblast furnaces at its Scunthorpe plant.
