OL,3,CParliament to vote on granting
OL,4,CGovernment control of British Steel
OL,6,FThe Commons sitting will begin at 11am
OL,7,Fand the House of Lords from midday in
OL,8,Fthe first parliamentary recall on a
OL,9,FSaturday since 1982, when MPs returned
OL,10,Fafter the start of the Falklands War.
OL,12,FOther significant recalls during
OL,13,Frecent years included a midweek
OL,14,Fsitting during the summer recess in
OL,15,FAugust 2021 to debate the evacuation
OL,16,Ffrom Afghanistan.
