OL,3,CParliament to vote on granting
OL,4,CGovernment control of British Steel
OL,6,FIn a letter to MPs shared with the PA
OL,7,Fnews agency, Commons Speaker Sir
OL,8,FLindsay Hoyle said he was satisfied
OL,9,Fthe "public interest" requires the
OL,10,Frecall to debate the Steel Industry
OL,11,F(Special Measures) Bill.
OL,13,FJingye, which bought British Steel in
OL,14,F2020, has said it invested more than
OL,15,F#1.2 billion to maintain operations
OL,16,Famid ongoing production instability
OL,17,Fand "significant" financial losses of
OL,18,Faround #700,000 a day.
