OL,3,CParliament to vote on granting
OL,4,CGovernment control of British Steel
OL,6,FThe Government says the new law would
OL,7,Fallow it to order raw materials for
OL,8,FScunthorpe's blast furnaces amid fears
OL,9,Fsupplies are on the brink of running
OL,10,Fout.
OL,12,FMinisters would be able to direct the
OL,13,Fcompany's board and workforce, and
OL,14,Fensure anyone at the plant "who takes
OL,15,Fsteps to keep it running, against the
OL,16,Forders of the Chinese ownership" can
OL,17,Fbe reinstated if they are sacked.
