OL,3,CParliament to vote on granting
OL,4,CGovernment control of British Steel
OL,6,FThe proposals to close Scunthorpe's
OL,7,Ffurnaces had sparked fears of job
OL,8,Flosses at the plant, which employs
OL,9,Fthousands of people.
OL,11,FBusiness Secretary Jonathan Reynolds
OL,12,Fsaid Jingye had confirmed the plans
OL,13,Fdespite months of talks and a #500
OL,14,Fmillion co-investment offer from
OL,15,FGovernment, leaving ministers "no
OL,16,Fchoice" but to act to spare job losses
OL,17,Fand save the plant.
